1
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:28,500
♪Heavens strike with thunderous wrath♪

2
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:32,180
♪Mountains and rivers shatter before my eyes♪

3
00:00:32,420 --> 00:00:35,500
♪Endless splendor cultivated through lifetimes♪

4
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:39,220
♪Turns to dust between my fingers in an instant♪

5
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:44,100
♪When the line between good and evil is clear♪

6
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:47,780
♪Countless souls drift into the boundless wilds♪

7
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:51,340
♪Carrying the spirit fire forward♪

8
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,340
♪I defy fate♪

9
00:00:53,580 --> 00:00:56,460
♪Just to remain by your side♪

10
00:00:57,340 --> 00:01:00,740
♪Falling into love's abyss♪

11
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:04,420
♪Like heavy rain pouring down♪

12
00:01:04,860 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Drunk on romance♪

13
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:11,980
♪In a blink, love and hate vanish into illusion♪

14
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:16,060
♪Falling into endless love♪

15
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:19,340
♪Stirring waves upending a lifetime♪

16
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:22,420
♪Even if this life leads to ruin♪

17
00:01:22,860 --> 00:01:26,460
♪I still choose to be entangled with you♪

18
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,100
♪Through all lifetimes♪

19
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:33,100
[When Destiny Brings The Demon]

20
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:36,500
[Based on the JJWXC novel "When Destiny Brings The Demon" by Fu Hua]

21
00:01:36,540 --> 00:01:39,420
[Episode 2]
[Struck by an NPC's Fate, But Can't Go AFK]

22
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:47,140
Chuhui's cultivation was so high, yet she failed the selection.

23
00:01:47,670 --> 00:01:50,980
Someone must've meddled with the process.

24
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,090
Please calm your anger, Madam.

25
00:01:52,670 --> 00:01:54,090
Among those chosen,

26
00:01:54,110 --> 00:01:55,700
is a disciple named Yu Rongrong.

27
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,220
Her skills are passable.

28
00:01:58,030 --> 00:01:59,530
If she and the chosen others

29
00:01:59,550 --> 00:02:00,620
can steal the Bloodseal Bloom,

30
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:03,290
it will grant Moon Palace millennia of cultivation.

31
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,290
Why worry?

32
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,670
Congratulations, Master.

33
00:02:12,300 --> 00:02:14,090
Anxue and Tan Muying made the cut,

34
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,460
just as we planned.

35
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:19,780
Never thought that slave-born Ye Ruling

36
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,410
would also be selected.

37
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,620
Though not as good as Anxue,

38
00:02:24,110 --> 00:02:26,090
she's the most gifted among the captives

39
00:02:26,110 --> 00:02:27,410
from the Demon Realm.

40
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:29,650
She'll be our second bargaining chip.

41
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:30,940
Mu Nisheng is exceptionally talented.

42
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,060
She'll surely fulfill your task.

43
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:34,220
As expected of your sisters,

44
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:38,650
Misses Xiyue and Wanqing made it in.

45
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:41,690
Once they bear Sima's children,

46
00:02:42,150 --> 00:02:43,370
we'll have the Spirit Fire

47
00:02:43,390 --> 00:02:44,780
in our own hands.

48
00:02:45,270 --> 00:02:48,340
Then all we need to do is kill Sima Jiao

49
00:02:48,830 --> 00:02:50,620
and take his place as master

50
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:52,130
of the Gengchen Celestial Palace.

51
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,570
Anyone here?

52
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:16,130
Nice spot.

53
00:03:17,430 --> 00:03:18,180
Not too high,

54
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:19,780
far from Central Tower.

55
00:03:20,670 --> 00:03:22,180
No colleagues dropping by.

56
00:03:23,390 --> 00:03:24,900
I'll lay down a thick quilt here

57
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:26,780
for my own luxury suite.

58
00:03:28,710 --> 00:03:30,130
[Stargazing Terrace, Three Saints Mountain]
Plenty of sunshine too.

59
00:03:30,830 --> 00:03:31,940
Much better

60
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,250
than the place I used to rent.

61
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:43,060
This Qiankun Pouch may be low-grade,

62
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,810
but it's more than enough

63
00:03:45,110 --> 00:03:46,090
for daily supplies.

64
00:03:46,390 --> 00:03:47,130
Remember:

65
00:03:47,390 --> 00:03:49,940
Don't make enemies in Three Saints Mountain.

66
00:03:50,390 --> 00:03:52,250
Just mind your own business

67
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:54,060
and never stick your neck out.

68
00:03:54,830 --> 00:03:56,460
Oh, Master...

69
00:03:57,110 --> 00:03:59,020
This isn't about showing off.

70
00:03:59,150 --> 00:04:01,060
I almost had my own funeral!

71
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,900
Wow, you can really hold a lot!

72
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:08,690
Such a tiny Qiankun Pouch, yet it holds so much!

73
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:11,180
I should've packed all my belongings.

74
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,860
Here's someone even bolder.

75
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,980
Surviving the big bad Grandmaster's wrath,

76
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:37,250
I'm truly blessed.

77
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,890
The one you went to all that trouble

78
00:04:40,910 --> 00:04:41,740
to send

79
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,250
is weaker than average

80
00:04:45,230 --> 00:04:47,620
and nothing special.

81
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:49,690
Still no news after all this time.

82
00:04:49,710 --> 00:04:50,450
All you need to know is,

83
00:04:50,470 --> 00:04:51,980
[Mingli, Demon Realm's Preceptor]
she's the only one who can kill Sima Jiao.

84
00:04:53,470 --> 00:04:55,570
If you have time to test me here,

85
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:56,890
better spend it thinking

86
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:59,450
how to use the Bone-Eroding Venom in her

87
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,180
to fulfill our pact sooner.

88
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:08,010
Didn't think I'd finally get it here,

89
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,130
my long-awaited vacation!

90
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,420
She's actually sleeping.

91
00:06:28,470 --> 00:06:30,940
Is Gengchen Celestial Palace sending her

92
00:06:31,230 --> 00:06:32,980
to provoke me on purpose,

93
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:35,300
or are they really this useless,

94
00:06:36,350 --> 00:06:38,940
not even realizing she's a Demon Realm spy?

95
00:06:40,470 --> 00:06:41,860
I'm innocent, Grandmaster...

96
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:48,770
Stupid snake.

97
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,210
Why would I get a headache

98
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:52,980
over a mere Demon Realm woman?

99
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:55,890
It's clearly the Spirit Fire in me acting up.

100
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:22,010
I want to see what she's really after.

101
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,620
How can she sleep so soundly?

102
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,660
Smelly.

103
00:07:45,910 --> 00:07:46,500
Let's go.

104
00:07:56,470 --> 00:07:57,690
Why didn't my alarm ring?

105
00:08:12,710 --> 00:08:14,450
These flowers are odd.

106
00:08:14,470 --> 00:08:16,010
They even glow at night.

107
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,660
Isn't that the girl

108
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:34,140
Grandmaster blasted away the other day?

109
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:12,580
[Lantern Pavilion, Gengchen Celestial Palace]

110
00:09:25,230 --> 00:09:25,730
Oh no!

111
00:09:26,350 --> 00:09:27,810
Yu Rongrong's life flame has gone out!

112
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:35,380
Return!

113
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:37,420
Luckily,

114
00:09:37,710 --> 00:09:39,180
her soul hasn't scattered yet.

115
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:40,570
Madam.

116
00:09:40,590 --> 00:09:42,570
I told you to be careful in all things.

117
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:43,940
How did you die so soon?

118
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,300
I died?

119
00:09:45,710 --> 00:09:48,140
I saw so many flowers at Grandmaster's place.

120
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,330
I just wanted to pick one,

121
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:51,020
and then I ended up here.

122
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,970
Could it be the Moonshade Bloom?

123
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:56,300
Madam Yue,

124
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:58,540
fortunately, our disciples

125
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:00,090
each get one chance at rebirth.

126
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,850
You'd best prepare

127
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,690
and send her on her way.

128
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,090
Two life lamps

129
00:10:12,990 --> 00:10:14,260
out in a single day.

130
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:17,810
Grandmaster is still as ruthless as ever.

131
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:20,060
He must still hold old grudges

132
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:23,660
and will vent them on the disciples.

133
00:10:25,590 --> 00:10:28,090
You think he cares about them?

134
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:31,690
He still remembers old scores with the Eight Palaces!

135
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,970
Back then, our fathers...

136
00:10:33,990 --> 00:10:35,940
I feel awful!

137
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,450
I feel awful!

138
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:37,900
Grandmaster!

139
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,570
I feel awful!

140
00:10:39,590 --> 00:10:40,660
- Grandmaster! - I feel awful...

141
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:41,140
Grandmaster.

142
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:44,260
Take this fire out of me.

143
00:10:44,350 --> 00:10:45,570
Bear it, Grandmaster.

144
00:10:45,590 --> 00:10:46,850
Let the blood out and it'll ease.

145
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,940
The Eight Palaces once drank his blood,

146
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:01,330
then locked him in Three Saints Mountain for 500 years.

147
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:04,570
His hatred only grows by the day.

148
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:08,140
If he shows no mercy to them,

149
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:10,690
imagine if he faces us directly,

150
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:14,850
he'll be even more ruthless.

151
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:16,810
Master Yin is right.

152
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:20,850
He means we should strike first.

153
00:11:21,440 --> 00:11:21,900
This...

154
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,570
With Spirit Fire in him,

155
00:11:31,350 --> 00:11:32,850
his power far exceeds ours.

156
00:11:33,990 --> 00:11:35,970
If we provoke him now,

157
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:39,490
we'll only die a miserable death.

158
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,800
Though he's forged a Spirit Fire avatar,

159
00:11:42,990 --> 00:11:45,550
the mountain's seal still holds.

160
00:11:45,830 --> 00:11:47,610
I urge you all

161
00:11:48,590 --> 00:11:50,330
not to act rashly.

162
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:57,570
Why do you think these disciples came?

163
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,810
They're just following orders from those old fools

164
00:11:59,830 --> 00:12:01,140
in Gengchen Celestial Palace,

165
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:05,210
here to take my blood and my life.

166
00:12:07,110 --> 00:12:08,540
They don't dare come here.

167
00:12:10,510 --> 00:12:11,180
Yet that one

168
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:14,020
strolls right in

169
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,610
and relaxes in my place.

170
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:18,570
Grandmaster...

171
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:19,420
Wait...

172
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,490
Grandmaster...

173
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:21,940
You're watching me.

174
00:12:22,040 --> 00:12:22,810
No.

175
00:12:22,830 --> 00:12:23,900
I'm just cross-eyed.

176
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:24,730
I was looking...

177
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:26,900
I was looking over there!

178
00:12:46,990 --> 00:12:47,730
Tell me,

179
00:12:48,280 --> 00:12:49,540
what are you really here for?

180
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:53,490
To fix my schedule and relax.

181
00:12:53,870 --> 00:12:55,090
In short, vacation.

182
00:12:58,710 --> 00:12:59,410
What's going on?

183
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,700
Why did my words change?

184
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:04,300
That guy's behind this!

185
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:06,690
This fantasy world even has a spell

186
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:09,210
that forces you to tell the truth!

187
00:13:11,710 --> 00:13:12,610
You don't want to kill me?

188
00:13:12,810 --> 00:13:13,420
No.

189
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,090
Why not?

190
00:13:15,110 --> 00:13:17,210
I'm just an innocent slacker.

191
00:13:17,470 --> 00:13:18,800
With cultivation this low,

192
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,730
why would I want to kill you?

193
00:13:26,350 --> 00:13:27,300
Really?

194
00:13:27,510 --> 00:13:28,330
What else?

195
00:13:28,590 --> 00:13:30,370
Are you scared of everything or what?

196
00:13:30,510 --> 00:13:31,540
Is your brain broken?

197
00:13:32,350 --> 00:13:32,940
I'm doomed.

198
00:13:33,110 --> 00:13:34,420
This spell is deadly.

199
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,180
Help!

200
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,730
Are you killing me or not?

201
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:46,420
Make it quick!

202
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:49,540
I wouldn't dare.

203
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:09,490
Has he been in seclusion so long

204
00:14:09,510 --> 00:14:10,850
that his mind's gone?

205
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:13,450
Gengchen Celestial Palace

206
00:14:13,470 --> 00:14:14,780
had it wrong from the start.

207
00:14:15,110 --> 00:14:16,850
Why send in disciples to serve him?

208
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:19,300
They should've sent a doctor

209
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,420
to fix his head.

210
00:14:41,230 --> 00:14:41,960
Get off.

211
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,690
Don't lick me, you mangy mutt.

212
00:14:56,870 --> 00:14:57,680
Mr. Snake,

213
00:14:57,920 --> 00:14:59,100
look at my scrawny arms and legs.

214
00:14:59,470 --> 00:15:00,420
Spare me, will you?

215
00:15:00,590 --> 00:15:02,060
I'd only get stuck in your teeth!

216
00:15:05,370 --> 00:15:06,790
You want to drink this?

217
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:10,350
You should've said so.

218
00:15:14,470 --> 00:15:15,300
Here you go.

219
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:19,610
Sorry about that.

220
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:20,810
I wasn't thinking.

221
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:22,810
Actually,

222
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,780
this is a specialty of our Serene Vale.

223
00:15:25,590 --> 00:15:27,140
This Spirit Bamboo

224
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:29,260
keeps producing Spirit Dew.

225
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:31,020
I usually drink it like milk tea.

226
00:15:31,630 --> 00:15:33,020
Didn't think you'd like it too.

227
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,810
Why's this snake acting like a dog?

228
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:44,660
To raise a giant serpent into a loyal hound...

229
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,850
Grandmaster truly lives up to his name.

230
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:57,330
Looks like I've bought myself another day?

231
00:16:09,350 --> 00:16:10,730
I feel awful!

232
00:16:10,750 --> 00:16:12,610
I feel awful!

233
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:14,260
I feel awful!

234
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:32,610
You dare drink something from the Demon Realm?

235
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,780
Tired of living, are you?

236
00:16:39,470 --> 00:16:41,380
Just because you ate with her twice,

237
00:16:42,040 --> 00:16:43,540
you're speaking up for her now?

238
00:16:46,230 --> 00:16:47,490
All men are greedy,

239
00:16:49,630 --> 00:16:51,140
let alone those from the Demon Realm.

240
00:16:52,230 --> 00:16:53,490
They either want the Spirit Fire

241
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:56,690
or covet the Bloodseal Bloom.

242
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:02,020
She's just better at pretending than the rest.

243
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:11,900
Aunt-Master Nisheng,

244
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:15,010
Yu Rongrong from Moon Palace vanished last night.

245
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:17,140
Not even a body was found.

246
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:20,250
And once you enter this mountain, you can't leave.

247
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:22,050
[Xiao Jincheng, Disciple of Heaven Palace]
No way back to the palace now...

248
00:17:23,790 --> 00:17:25,970
No one can guess Grandmaster's temper.

249
00:17:25,990 --> 00:17:26,690
Don't panic yet.

250
00:17:27,750 --> 00:17:28,580
No matter what,

251
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:30,550
staying alive is what matters.

252
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,340
If one of us

253
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:34,580
can win Grandmaster's favor

254
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:35,770
and become his consort,

255
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:37,810
our Heaven Palace

256
00:17:38,070 --> 00:17:39,680
will rise to lead the Eight Palaces.

257
00:17:40,310 --> 00:17:42,730
Sima Jiao is just as the Master said,

258
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:43,770
cruel and lawless.

259
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:46,010
We must find his weakness

260
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,490
and kill him as soon as possible.

261
00:17:47,790 --> 00:17:50,420
The Fengshan Spirit Fire has merged with Sima Jiao.

262
00:17:50,420 --> 00:17:51,230
[Tan Muying, Disciple of Yin Palace]

263
00:17:51,230 --> 00:17:52,420
If Sima Jiao dies,

264
00:17:52,750 --> 00:17:53,970
the Spirit Fire will go out too.

265
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:55,450
Then

266
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:56,970
all of Gengchen Celestial Palace

267
00:17:56,990 --> 00:17:58,290
will lose its spiritual energy.

268
00:17:58,600 --> 00:17:59,530
How will we cultivate?

269
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:01,770
The Bloodseal Bloom is grown by the Spirit Fire

270
00:18:01,790 --> 00:18:03,820
feeding on Sima Jiao's blood.

271
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:06,420
Eat the Bloom and his blood,

272
00:18:06,790 --> 00:18:08,380
and we can still raise our power.

273
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,450
Have you forgotten what the Master said?

274
00:18:11,270 --> 00:18:12,820
Back then, he offended Sima Jiao.

275
00:18:13,230 --> 00:18:14,140
If one day

276
00:18:14,440 --> 00:18:16,290
Sima Jiao decides to settle old scores,

277
00:18:17,070 --> 00:18:18,860
we'll all die miserably.

278
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:21,100
What cultivation's left?

279
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:23,490
So, you called me here

280
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,080
just to discuss

281
00:18:25,510 --> 00:18:26,820
this impossible task?

282
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:28,380
Ye Ruling,

283
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:31,140
stop acting like it's none of your business.

284
00:18:31,470 --> 00:18:32,250
Don't forget

285
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:35,900
your clansmen are still in the Master's hands.

286
00:18:48,030 --> 00:18:49,970
I've prepared this for Mr. Snake.

287
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:53,140
Hope he won't wake me tonight

288
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:54,660
so I can get a good night's sleep.

289
00:19:11,710 --> 00:19:14,190
Why does this feel so familiar?

290
00:19:15,230 --> 00:19:17,250
Do cultivators get period cramps too?

291
00:19:20,750 --> 00:19:21,900
It hurts so much...

292
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:25,100
Why's it getting worse?

293
00:19:31,030 --> 00:19:31,940
Didn't Mingli say

294
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,690
this Companion Bell can trigger

295
00:19:33,710 --> 00:19:35,050
Liao Tingyan's Bone-Eroding Venom?

296
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:41,490
Why has she shown no reaction

297
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:42,660
after hearing the call?

298
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:45,100
Does she really think

299
00:19:45,840 --> 00:19:47,900
that by clinging to Sima Jiao,

300
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:49,660
she can escape our control?

301
00:19:52,470 --> 00:19:53,010
Fine.

302
00:19:54,470 --> 00:19:56,290
Let's see how long you can survive

303
00:19:56,990 --> 00:19:58,450
this Bone-Eroding Venom!

304
00:20:54,270 --> 00:20:55,140
Stupid snake,

305
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:58,100
what did you bring back?

306
00:21:13,840 --> 00:21:15,180
She's been poisoned by demonic venom.

307
00:21:19,600 --> 00:21:20,620
Why do you want to save her?

308
00:21:20,960 --> 00:21:22,670
Do you even know why she's here?

309
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:26,180
You brought her to me this cluelessly?

310
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:27,700
Are you looking to die?

311
00:21:32,510 --> 00:21:33,210
This poison

312
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:35,050
is just a demonic trick

313
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:37,450
to control puppets.

314
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:58,100
She actually fell asleep.

315
00:22:01,510 --> 00:22:03,420
The Demon Realm went to all that trouble,

316
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:06,690
only to send someone like this?

317
00:22:07,510 --> 00:22:08,180
Looks like

318
00:22:08,710 --> 00:22:10,210
she's smarter than those other fools.

319
00:22:11,310 --> 00:22:12,940
Instead of rushing to my face to die,

320
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:15,420
she won over that stupid snake.

321
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,860
Such deep scheming

322
00:22:20,990 --> 00:22:22,050
suits that face.

323
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:11,620
Grandmaster...

324
00:23:24,030 --> 00:23:27,140
Why am I in your hall?

325
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:33,340
Nice act.

326
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:37,210
You dared use that stupid snake

327
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:39,530
to bring you to my Central Tower?

328
00:23:42,230 --> 00:23:44,580
Maybe I passed out last night

329
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:45,730
from the stomach pain.

330
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:46,970
I guess Mr. Snake got worried

331
00:23:47,310 --> 00:23:48,530
and wanted you to save me.

332
00:23:48,960 --> 00:23:50,620
I didn't mean to trouble you.

333
00:23:53,230 --> 00:23:54,250
My stomach doesn't hurt anymore?

334
00:23:55,360 --> 00:23:56,210
You drank my blood.

335
00:23:57,230 --> 00:23:58,210
Of course it won't hurt.

336
00:23:59,120 --> 00:24:01,100
I drank your blood?

337
00:24:05,990 --> 00:24:07,250
If you dare spit it out, I'll kill you.

338
00:24:13,230 --> 00:24:15,490
Your blood even works as a painkiller?

339
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:17,860
Not only eases pain,

340
00:24:19,470 --> 00:24:20,820
it boosts cultivation too.

341
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:22,450
No one in this world doesn't want it.

342
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:24,140
Count me out.

343
00:24:24,840 --> 00:24:25,900
I'm not that interested.

344
00:24:33,990 --> 00:24:35,210
Looking at you now

345
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:37,970
makes me want to finish you on the spot.

346
00:24:42,430 --> 00:24:43,240
No...

347
00:24:43,600 --> 00:24:44,490
I...

348
00:24:44,510 --> 00:24:46,250
I may dirty your hands...

349
00:25:01,790 --> 00:25:03,140
If it hurt that much,

350
00:25:05,470 --> 00:25:07,010
