351
00:25:07,990 --> 00:25:10,450
Because no reason, no grudge.

352
00:25:19,310 --> 00:25:20,660
In this world,

353
00:25:21,470 --> 00:25:22,620
killing doesn't need a grudge,

354
00:25:24,990 --> 00:25:26,210
much less a reason.

355
00:25:28,310 --> 00:25:29,100
Like right now,

356
00:25:30,360 --> 00:25:31,900
no grudge, no reason,

357
00:25:32,710 --> 00:25:34,100
I just want to kill you.

358
00:25:36,990 --> 00:25:38,010
And what can you do about it?

359
00:25:39,030 --> 00:25:40,210
Nothing.

360
00:25:40,230 --> 00:25:41,530
I can't beat you anyway.

361
00:26:04,070 --> 00:26:04,970
You want me to kill you?

362
00:26:06,750 --> 00:26:07,970
Well, I won't.

363
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,210
From now on,

364
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:17,860
you'll serve me.

365
00:26:20,960 --> 00:26:21,730
Me?

366
00:26:30,790 --> 00:26:31,970
I'm leaving now.

367
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:48,490
No grudge...

368
00:26:51,470 --> 00:26:52,380
no reason...

369
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:55,530
so she won't kill me?

370
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:06,010
Everyone in Gengchen Celestial Palace is after my blood.

371
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:09,620
If not for the fact that only I can feed the Spirit Fire,

372
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:15,210
if not for the Spirit Fire nourishing the whole palace,

373
00:27:17,070 --> 00:27:18,730
if not for the fact they can't defeat me,

374
00:27:19,750 --> 00:27:21,660
I'd have been torn apart long ago.

375
00:27:23,840 --> 00:27:25,970
The Demon Realm has always wanted to destroy this palace

376
00:27:27,120 --> 00:27:28,250
and extinguish the Spirit Fire.

377
00:27:29,990 --> 00:27:31,420
They should want to kill me.

378
00:27:32,470 --> 00:27:33,010
So why...

379
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:35,820
doesn't she want to?

380
00:27:36,400 --> 00:27:38,770
After such a nerve-racking day,

381
00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:41,900
I won't sleep well tonight.

382
00:27:51,840 --> 00:27:52,900
Ridiculous.

383
00:27:53,510 --> 00:27:56,340
The Truth Spell never lies.

384
00:27:58,160 --> 00:27:59,530
If she truly has no intent to kill,

385
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:02,860
perhaps I can use her.

386
00:28:05,750 --> 00:28:06,530
Five hundred years...

387
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:09,770
the night of the new moon.

388
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:16,010
Aunt-Master,

389
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:18,770
[Central Tower, Three Saints Mountain]
we've waited here every day,

390
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:21,860
but this door has never opened for us.

391
00:28:22,550 --> 00:28:23,450
Will Grandmaster

392
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:25,140
really see us?

393
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:28,420
Don't tell me you're as shallow as the others.

394
00:28:28,710 --> 00:28:29,580
If you're afraid,

395
00:28:29,710 --> 00:28:30,290
then leave.

396
00:28:30,470 --> 00:28:31,380
No, Aunt-Master.

397
00:28:31,990 --> 00:28:34,660
I just don't know how to face Grandmaster.

398
00:28:35,990 --> 00:28:37,010
The Master once said

399
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,940
that before this Grandmaster,

400
00:28:39,470 --> 00:28:41,490
it's impossible to hide anything.

401
00:28:42,160 --> 00:28:43,730
All we need is the most humble

402
00:28:44,070 --> 00:28:45,290
and devout posture,

403
00:28:45,790 --> 00:28:47,420
laying all our thoughts bare to him.

404
00:28:47,990 --> 00:28:49,450
As long as I keep trying,

405
00:28:50,230 --> 00:28:52,420
Grandmaster will be moved by me.

406
00:28:57,790 --> 00:29:00,210
Mr. Snake really meant well but made trouble.

407
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:02,940
I haven't even rested a few days,

408
00:29:03,960 --> 00:29:05,050
and it's back to work.

409
00:29:08,070 --> 00:29:09,530
I'm here to pay respects to you.

410
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:12,050
Please accept me, Grandmaster.

411
00:29:16,270 --> 00:29:17,970
She's a brave one,

412
00:29:18,710 --> 00:29:20,250
volunteering to face

413
00:29:20,270 --> 00:29:21,690
that moody grandmaster.

414
00:29:22,600 --> 00:29:24,530
No wonder she can lead the group.

415
00:29:25,070 --> 00:29:27,420
Her mindset is really something.

416
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:30,250
Wish I could trade places with her.

417
00:29:39,360 --> 00:29:40,530
You're still alive?

418
00:29:41,360 --> 00:29:42,970
What's wrong with you people?

419
00:29:43,790 --> 00:29:45,140
Everyone asks me the same thing.

420
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:46,820
I'm not dying.

421
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,180
I'm staying alive.

422
00:29:49,230 --> 00:29:50,380
If you want to stay alive,

423
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:52,770
keep your distance from here.

424
00:29:53,510 --> 00:29:54,900
I'd love to.

425
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:03,490
What's with Grandmaster?

426
00:30:04,510 --> 00:30:05,420
He asks me to work here

427
00:30:05,440 --> 00:30:06,490
without even giving me a pass.

428
00:30:06,510 --> 00:30:07,380
How am I supposed to get in?

429
00:30:08,510 --> 00:30:09,140
Aunt-Master,

430
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:11,970
she probably doesn't know Grandmaster's temper.

431
00:30:12,470 --> 00:30:13,450
Should we warn her?

432
00:30:13,790 --> 00:30:14,770
Why meddle?

433
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:16,940
The only ones safe this close

434
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,180
