435
00:30:18,710 --> 00:30:21,140
She'll probably die under this tower today.

436
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:26,060
Grandmaster, I'm here for work!

437
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:31,210
How...

438
00:30:31,750 --> 00:30:32,340
how is this possible?

439
00:30:35,120 --> 00:30:36,580
You just knock and it opens?

440
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:38,580
How did she get in?

441
00:30:56,470 --> 00:30:59,580
What will Grandmaster have me do?

442
00:30:59,600 --> 00:31:00,340
What's in that bag?

443
00:31:06,990 --> 00:31:08,420
These are just

444
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:09,770
my everyday essentials.

445
00:31:10,310 --> 00:31:12,250
I took them out of my Qiankun Pouch.

446
00:31:12,600 --> 00:31:14,530
I'm not great with spiritual power.

447
00:31:14,550 --> 00:31:16,050
I can only take things out,

448
00:31:16,200 --> 00:31:17,340
not put them in.

449
00:31:17,510 --> 00:31:18,770
Drop your junk

450
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:19,900
and follow me.

451
00:31:40,310 --> 00:31:40,970
Grandmaster,

452
00:31:41,550 --> 00:31:45,210
is that person outside dead?

453
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:46,770
What do you think?

454
00:31:49,070 --> 00:31:50,450
Why kill her?

455
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:54,140
Worse than obvious greed,

456
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,210
I hate

457
00:31:57,230 --> 00:31:59,490
mindless puppets with no soul.

458
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:03,690
Killing her didn't even interest me.

459
00:32:05,270 --> 00:32:06,900
Then why?

460
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:08,450
She was too noisy

461
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:13,250
and got on my nerves.

462
00:32:14,120 --> 00:32:16,250
You kill over annoyance?

463
00:32:17,120 --> 00:32:19,100
This grandmaster's crazy.

464
00:32:30,990 --> 00:32:32,210
I'm exhausted.

465
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:35,050
This is worse than rush hour.

466
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:46,420
You can't go on?

467
00:32:48,230 --> 00:32:48,900
Grandmaster,

468
00:32:49,750 --> 00:32:51,140
may I ask

469
00:32:51,550 --> 00:32:52,730
why we are

470
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:55,100
climbing this high?

471
00:32:55,840 --> 00:32:56,580
No reason.

472
00:32:58,400 --> 00:33:01,250
Looks like he's just too bored

473
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:03,100
