483
00:34:03,340 --> 00:34:04,040
Grandmaster,

484
00:34:04,310 --> 00:34:05,490
I'm working hard!

485
00:34:05,550 --> 00:34:06,380
I'm getting things done!

486
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:15,380
Oh, Mr. Snake, it's you.

487
00:34:16,030 --> 00:34:18,130
